1. If You Want To Know, Which Machine You Are Using

# hostname

2. For Checking Ip Address For Machine

# ifconfig

(This will show details about all network interfaces, like IP address, MAC address, etc)

3. If You Only Need The System's Ip Address

# hostname -i

4. To Check The Linux Version You Are Using

# cat /etc/os-release

(output- os version will show on the screen)
